my_nicegui_app/
│── app/
│   ├── __init__.py        # Make the folder a package
│   ├── main.py            # Entry point (start NiceGUI here)
│   ├── routes.py          # Define UI routes (optional)
│   ├── views/
│   │   ├── __init__.py    
│   │   ├── home.py        # Home page UI
│   │   ├── dashboard.py   # Dashboard page UI
│   │   ├── settings.py    # Settings page UI
│   ├── components/        # Custom reusable UI components
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── navbar.py      # Navigation bar component
│   │   ├── footer.py      # Footer component
│   ├── services/          # Business logic (e.g., database, API calls)
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── database.py    # DB connection and queries
│   │   ├── auth.py        # Authentication logic
│   ├── static/            # Static assets (images, CSS, etc.)
│   ├── templates/         # Optional Jinja templates if needed
│
│── tests/                 # Unit and integration tests
│   ├── test_main.py
│   ├── test_views.py
│
│── .env                   # Environment variables
│── pyproject.toml          # Managed by `uv`
│── README.md               # Project documentation
│── .gitignore              # Ignore unnecessary files
│── run.py                  # Simple script to run the app

https://github.com/bitdoze/nicegui-starter
